(1, 'Post From James Bhatta', 'post-from-james-bhatta', '<p class=\"project-section-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\"><h2 class=\"hckui__typography__h2 title-with-anchor\" style=\"font-family: DINPro, sans-serif; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">Story</h2></p><p class=\"project-story collapsed hljs-active hljs-monokai\" itemprop=\"text\"><h3 class=\"hckui__typography__h3 title-with-anchor\" id=\"toc-introduction-0\" style=\"font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://www.hackster.io/bluetiger9/lora-to-ethernet-gateway-ff9684#toc-introduction-0\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;#toc-introduction-0&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230); margin-left: -22px; padding-right: 5px; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;\"><span class=\"fa fa-link\"></span></a>Introduction</h3><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">I got some LoRa modules with SPI communication interface. One of the options it would have been to connect them to my Raspberry Pi. But, I didn\'t really liked the idea because I already had some stuff connected to my Raspberry Pi, and this starts getting unmanageable.</p><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">So, I decided to create a LoRa-to-Ethernet gateway that can be connected directly to a home router. The WIZ750SR module with its Ethernet interface and Cortex-M0 SoC was a great candidate to implement such a device.</p><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">Here are some pictures with the resulting LoRa-to-Ethernet Gateway:</p><p data-hypernova-key=\"ImageCarousel\" data-hypernova-id=\"3f712e63-4dc0-4982-87c4-56256f32fa49\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p data-reactroot=\"\"><p class=\"image_carousel__container__hMJxn\" style=\"width: 615px; height: 372px; margin: 30px 0px;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__wrapper__102VA\" style=\"position: relative; height: 342px; user-select: none; width: 615px;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__navAreaLeft__1PU4a image_carousel__navArea__2Ef8D\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; height: 342px; width: 92.25px; position: absolute; top: 0px; cursor: pointer; z-index: 1; left: 0px; user-select: none;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__hoverHighlightLeft__1S9h7 image_carousel__hoverHighlight__1YVDQ\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin-left: 5px; user-select: none;\"><svg class=\"image_carousel__navArrowLeft__5F8Rp image_carousel__navArrow__310yF\" viewBox=\"0 0 15 26\" width=\"15px\" height=\"15px\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><polyline stroke=\"\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" points=\"1 1 13 13.0299571 1 25\"></polyline></svg></p></p><p class=\"image_carousel__navAreaRight__2Fd8H image_carousel__navArea__2Ef8D\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-end; height: 342px; width: 92.25px; position: absolute; top: 0px; cursor: pointer; z-index: 1; right: 0px; user-select: none;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__hoverHighlightRight__2MeJj image_carousel__hoverHighlight__1YVDQ\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; width: 40px; height: 40px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 5px; user-select: none;\"><svg class=\"image_carousel__navArrowRight__HvDjb image_carousel__navArrow__310yF\" viewBox=\"0 0 15 26\" width=\"15px\" height=\"15px\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><polyline stroke=\"\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" points=\"1 1 13 13.0299571 1 25\"></polyline></svg></p></p><p class=\"image_carousel__scrollContainer__3mmPE \" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; width: 615px; height: 342px; overflow: auto; user-select: none;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__imageContainer__22WPm\" style=\"min-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 325.2px; user-select: none;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__imageWrapper__39AG2\" style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 325.2px; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; max-width: 960px; user-select: none;\"><img class=\"image_carousel__image__2-CjO \" src=\"https://hackster.imgix.net/uploads/attachments/509317/20180624_180836_DeHAl0qVoG.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;w=680&amp;h=510&amp;fit=max\" alt=\"\" style=\"color: transparent; cursor: zoom-in; max-height: 100%; user-select: none;\"></p></p><p class=\"image_carousel__imageContainer__22WPm\" style=\"min-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 325.2px; user-select: none;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__imageWrapper__39AG2\" style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 325.2px; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; max-width: 960px; user-select: none;\"><img class=\"image_carousel__image__2-CjO \" src=\"https://hackster.imgix.net/uploads/attachments/509320/20180624_181610_r8mV6g2AEz.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;w=680&amp;h=510&amp;fit=max\" alt=\"\" style=\"color: transparent; cursor: zoom-in; max-height: 100%; user-select: none;\"></p></p><p class=\"image_carousel__imageContainer__22WPm\" style=\"min-width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 325.2px; user-select: none;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__imageWrapper__39AG2\" style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 325.2px; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; max-width: 960px; user-select: none;\"><img class=\"image_carousel__image__2-CjO \" src=\"https://hackster.imgix.net/uploads/attachments/509311/20180624_181725_inx5X20Ey2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;w=680&amp;h=510&amp;fit=max\" style=\"color: transparent; cursor: zoom-in; max-height: 100%; user-select: none;\"></p></p></p></p><p class=\"image_carousel__caption__2sZrD\" style=\"color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px; text-align: center; user-select: none;\"><span style=\"user-select: none;\">3 / 3</span><span style=\"user-select: none;\"></span></p></p></p></p><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">But, lets see how we got here...</p><h3 class=\"hckui__typography__h3 title-with-anchor\" id=\"toc-lora-1\" style=\"font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://www.hackster.io/bluetiger9/lora-to-ethernet-gateway-ff9684#toc-lora-1\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;#toc-lora-1&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230); margin-left: -22px; padding-right: 5px; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;\"><span class=\"fa fa-link\"></span></a>LoRa</h3><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">LoRa is relatively new long-range low-power wireless technology.</p><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">According to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LoRa\" class=\"hckui__typography__linkBlue\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Wikipedia&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/LoRa&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230);\">Wikipedia</a>,</p><blockquote style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">LoRa uses license-free sub-gigahertz radio frequency bands like 169 MHz, 433 MHz, 868 MHz (Europe) and 915 MHz (North America). LoRa enables very-long-range transmissions (more than 10 km in rural areas) with low power consumption. The technology is presented in two parts — LoRa, the physical layer and LoRaWAN, the upper layers.</blockquote><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">In this project I implemented an Ethernet interface for the LoRa physical layer. This has the advantage that allows just using the LoRa PHY with our custom messages, but also allows implementing&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lora-alliance.org/about-lorawan\" class=\"hckui__typography__linkBlue\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;LoRaWAN&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://lora-alliance.org/about-lorawan&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230);\">LoRaWAN</a>&nbsp;if we want so.</p><h3 class=\"hckui__typography__h3 title-with-anchor\" id=\"toc-the-lora-modules-2\" style=\"font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px;\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"https://www.hackster.io/bluetiger9/lora-to-ethernet-gateway-ff9684#toc-the-lora-modules-2\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;#toc-the-lora-modules-2&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230); margin-left: -22px; padding-right: 5px; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;\"><span class=\"fa fa-link\"></span></a>The LoRa modules</h3><p class=\"hckui__typography__bodyL\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(74, 74, 74); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif;\">I used two 433 MHz modules purchased from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.aliexpress.com/item/2pcs-RF-LoRa-module-SX1278-chip-PM1280-Long-Distance-communication-Receiver-and-Transmitter-SPI-LORA-IOT/32699425331.html?spm=a2g0s.9042311.0.0.4e714c4d1BTenc\" class=\"hckui__typography__linkBlue\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;AliExpress&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://www.aliexpress.com/item/2pcs-RF-LoRa-module-SX1278-chip-PM1280-Long-Distance-communication-Receiver-and-Transmitter-SPI-LORA-IOT/32699425331.html?spm=a2g0s.9042311.0.0.4e714c4d1BTenc&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230);\">AliExpress</a>. The boards are powered by the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.semtech.com/products/wireless-rf/lora-transceivers/SX1278\" class=\"hckui__typography__linkBlue\" data-ha=\"{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Clicked link&quot;,&quot;customProps&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;Semtech SX1278&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://www.semtech.com/products/wireless-rf/lora-transceivers/SX1278&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;story&quot;,&quot;location&quot;:&quot;story&quot;},&quot;clickOpts&quot;:{&quot;delayRedirect&quot;:true}}\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color: rgb(46, 159, 230);\">Semtech SX1278</a>&nbsp;chip.</p><p data-hypernova-key=\"ImageCarousel\" data-hypernova-id=\"3c99d7c2-73e1-47c3-bd77-75978adfca27\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: proxima-nova, HelveticaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p data-reactroot=\"\"><p class=\"image_carousel__container__hMJxn\" style=\"width: 615px; height: 540px; margin: 30px 0px;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__wrapper__102VA\" style=\"position: relative; height: 510px; user-select: none; width: 615px;\"><p class=\"image_carousel__navAreaLeft__1PU4a image_carousel__navArea__2Ef8D\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; height: 510px; width: 92.25px; position: