0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The AudioMod Smart Power Reserve charging case is a battery case for the iPhone 8 and 8 Plus that also includes a headphone jack. There are also versions of the&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon: iPhone 7 AudioMod Smart Battery Case \" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FAudioMod-Battery-Headphone-4100mAh-Technology-iPhone-X%2Fdp%2FB076VXGHFH%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">iPhone 7</a>(£69.99/US$69.99) and&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon: Encased iPhone 7 Plus Battery Case\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAudioMod-Battery-Headphone-4100mAh-Technology-iPhone-X%2Fdp%2FB07DXJ4Q41%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">7 Plus</a>&nbsp;(US only, $69.99), and the&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon: iPhone X AudioMod Smart Battery Case\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FAudioMod-Battery-Headphone-4100mAh-Technology-iPhone-X%2Fdp%2FB076VY7H1N%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">iPhone X</a>&nbsp;(£69.95/$69.99).</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">Audiomod has a solution for wired headphone fans that not only re-introduces the 3.5mm headphone jack but serves as a battery pack that also protects your phone.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The headphone port allows for both straight and shorter angled jacks, and works well. It supports the Mic/Volume/Play/Pause/Skip functions.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The case is a two-piece design. You slip the phone into the case and then attach a top part to create the all-round case protection. It feels sturdy and, while not thin, isn\'t overly bulky. It weighs 115g.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The recharging battery is a decent capacity (3,000mAh) that will boost your fading iPhone by at least a full charge. At the back is the recharge button and a four-LED power indicator. It features the usual cutouts for camera and buttons.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">Our only gripe is that the case charges not with a Lightning connector but fiddly MicroUSB. AudioMod cases comes with a 5 year manufacturer\'s warranty.&nbsp;</p></p><p class=\"compItem np\" id=\"toc-3664903-6\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: noto_serifregular;\"><h4 class=\"productName \" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 30px 0px 0px; font-family: noto_sansbold; font-size: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18); clear: both;\">Anker PowerCore Case for iPhone 7</h4><span class=\"reviewImage \" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; float: right; max-width: 50%; height: auto; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: none;\"><a class=\"lightboxGallery\" href=\"https://cdn2.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/anker-battery-case-iphone-7_thumb800.jpg\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18); cursor: zoom-in !important;\"><img class=\"lightbox lazyloaded\" alt=\"Anker PowerCore Case for iPhone 7\" src=\"https://cdn2.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/anker-battery-case-iphone-7_thumb800.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn2.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/anker-battery-case-iphone-7_thumb800.jpg\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: block;\"></a></span><ul class=\"spec-6 product-spec\" data-product-name=\"Anker PowerCore Case for iPhone 7\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data-price-eu_gb=\"£99.99\" data-price-eu_fr=\"\" data-price-eu_es=\"\" data-price-us=\"\" data-price-eu=\"\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: noto_serifbold;\">RRP:</span>&nbsp;£99.99</li></ul><section id=\"affiliate-table-container-1A1731B3-23DB-42D0-9AB24200B15D8FF4\" class=\"affiliate-links-container affiliate-links-container--pca affiliate-links-container--loaded\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><ul class=\"affiliate-links\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"></ul></section><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">Another case that works with all (non-Plus-sized) iPhones from the 6s through to the 8 is the Anker PowerCore that features a large back camera cutout across the width of the phone.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">Its battery capacity is 2,200mAh – above the iPhone 8’s own battery but a little below the Apple and Mophie cases. But it is Apple certified, unlike some of the battery cases tested here that offer larger capacities.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The one-piece PowerCore feels much like the Apple case, and is actually one of the lightest we tested, at just 68g. However, it connects to the iPhone not though a static integrated Lightning connector but via a dangly cable that you plug in when you need to recharge the phone from the case.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The Anker PowerCore is a lot cheaper than the Apple Smart Case - it’s just&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FBattery-Anker-PowerCore-Capacity-Certified%2Fdp%2FB01N5LP0VU%2F%3Ftag%3Dpcagenius-21%26ascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">£29.99 on Amazon UK</a>.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The case itself charges via MicroUSB cable (included).</p></p><p class=\"compItem np\" id=\"toc-3664903-7\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: noto_serifregular;\"><h4 class=\"productName \" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 30px 0px 0px; font-family: noto_sansbold; font-size: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18); clear: both;\">Runsy iPhone 8 /7 / 6s / 6 Battery Case</h4><span class=\"reviewImage \" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; float: right; max-width: 50%; height: auto; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: none;\"><a class=\"lightboxGallery\" href=\"https://cdn1.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/runsy-iphone-battery-case_thumb800.jpg\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18); cursor: zoom-in !important;\"><img class=\"lightbox lazyloaded\" alt=\"Runsy iPhone 8 /7 / 6s / 6 Battery Case\" src=\"https://cdn1.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/runsy-iphone-battery-case_thumb800.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn1.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/runsy-iphone-battery-case_thumb800.jpg\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: block;\"></a></span><ul class=\"spec-7 product-spec\" data-product-name=\"Runsy iPhone 8 /7 / 6s / 6 Battery Case\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data-price-eu_gb=\"£44.99\" data-price-eu_fr=\"\" data-price-eu_es=\"\" data-price-us=\"34.99\" data-price-eu=\"\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: noto_serifbold;\">RRP:</span>&nbsp;US$34.99</li></ul><section id=\"affiliate-table-container-38D5934D-937A-489A-935C29145BFB15C0\" class=\"affiliate-links-container affiliate-links-container--pca affiliate-links-container--loaded\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><ul class=\"affiliate-links\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"></ul></section><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">Much heavier and a fair bit bulkier is the Runsy Battery Case, which weighs in at 137g. This extra heft is no doubt due to the giant 5,800mAh battery capacity.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The case is a two-part design, which we found a little fiddly, but the phone should live inside the case most of the time so shouldn’t be a problem. We also weren’t rather concerned by the internal unofficial-looking Lightning connector that looked like it would impale the iPhone’s charging slot. The case did charge the phone, though.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">In fact, you can charge a second phone while your iPhone 8 charges, using the USB cable (not included).</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The big case features a little stand so you can use it to prop up the phone when watching a video, and also a fully sized USB slot that can be used to attach a second phone so that you can charge two at once!</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">At&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB06XDBRRW9%2Fref%3Doh_aui_detailpage_o02_s00%3Fie%3DUTF8%26tag%3Dpcad03-21%26ascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">£29.99&nbsp;on Amazon UK</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRUNSY-Rechargeable-Extended-Charging-External%2Fdp%2FB06XDBRRW9%2F%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">$34.99 on Amazon US</a>&nbsp;for iPhone 8, and&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FRUNSY-Rechargeable-Extended-Charging-External-5-5-inch%2Fdp%2FB06XCWQXJL%2Fref%3Dsr_1_2%3Fie%3DUTF8%26tag%3Dpcad03-21%26ascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">£34.99</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRUNSY-Rechargeable-Extended-Charging-External%2Fdp%2FB06XCWQXJL%2F%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">$39.99 in the US</a>&nbsp;for 8 Plus, it’s certainly one of the cheaper battery cases that works with the iPhone 8, but it’s a big old brute of a case.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The Runsy might appeal to the long-haul traveller or very demanding users who require such a large backup battery during the day, but for casual users who want a little extra battery life plus phone protection this is probably over the top.</p></p><p class=\"compItem np\" id=\"toc-3664903-8\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: noto_serifregular;\"><h4 class=\"productName \" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 30px 0px 0px; font-family: noto_sansbold; font-size: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18); clear: both;\">Nekteck iPhone 7 / 8 Battery Case</h4><span class=\"reviewImage \" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px; float: right; max-width: 50%; height: auto; overflow: hidden; border-bottom: none;\"><a class=\"lightboxGallery\" href=\"https://cdn3.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/nektech-iphone--battery-case_thumb800.jpg\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18); cursor: zoom-in !important;\"><img class=\"lightbox lazyloaded\" alt=\"Nekteck iPhone 7 / 8 Battery Case\" src=\"https://cdn3.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/nektech-iphone--battery-case_thumb800.jpg\" data-src=\"https://cdn3.techadvisor.co.uk/cmsdata/slideshow/3664903/nektech-iphone--battery-case_thumb800.jpg\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: block;\"></a></span><ul class=\"spec-8 product-spec\" data-product-name=\"Nekteck iPhone 7 / 8 Battery Case\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"><li data-price-eu_gb=\"£25\" data-price-eu_fr=\"\" data-price-eu_es=\"\" data-price-us=\"$19.99\" data-price-eu=\"\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: noto_serifbold;\">RRP:</span>&nbsp;$19.99</li></ul><section id=\"affiliate-table-container-D586C925-7F07-4D2D-B0637B58B43A94B4\" class=\"affiliate-links-container affiliate-links-container--pca affiliate-links-container--loaded\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><ul class=\"affiliate-links\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\"></ul></section><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The Nektech battery case does feature an Apple-certified Lightning connector, which is more reassuring than the other cheaper cases we tested.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">Its 3,100mAh battery capacity should give you a full recharge, but is not as giant as the other cheaper cases here – but bigger than the Apple and Mophie battery cases.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">It’s one-piece design is at the bulkier and heavier (111g) end of the range. If used just for travelling rather than everyday use then you shouldn’t balk at this added bulk.</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">There’s an LED strip at the back to let you know how much charge is left in the case. You recharge via a MicroUSB cable (included).</p><p style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7em;\">The Nektech Battery Case costs roughly&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon: Nekteck iPhone 7/8 Battery Case\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB06XHYZ9PJ%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">£26 on Amazon UK</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon US: Nekteck iPhone 7/8 Battery Case\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNekteck-certified-Connector-External-Protective%2Fdp%2FB06XHYZ9PJ%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">$29.99 on Amazon US</a>&nbsp;for iPhone 8; for the 8 Plus model its costs roughly&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon: Nekteck iPhone 8 Plus\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.uk%2FNekteck-certified-Connector-External-Charging%2Fdp%2FB01N7CI55T%2F%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">£30 in the UK</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Amazon US: Nekteck iPhone 8 Plus/7 Plus Battery Case\" href=\"https://buy.geni.us/Proxy.ashx?TSID=13303&amp;GR_URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNekteck-certified-Connector-External-Charging%2Fdp%2FB01N7CI55T%2F%3Fascsubtag%3D06-3664903-11-0000000\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"outline: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(205, 9, 18);\">$19 in the US</a>.</p></p>', 'complete-confirmation-1530279378.jpg', 'This is a sample text for the overlay. It does not contain anything fancy to read. But thanks for reading.', 1, '2018-06-29 09:51:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0);
