(20, '1.1 Computer Organization and Computer Architecture', '11-computer-organization-and-computer-architecture', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Computer\r\norganization is concerned with the way the hardware component operate and the\r\nway they are connected together to form computer system.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">While\r\ncomputer architecture is concerned with the structure and the behavior of the\r\ncomputer system. It includes information formats, instruction set and\r\ntechniques for addressing memory.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Architecture\r\ndescribes what the computer does and organization describes how computer does\r\nit.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Architecture\r\nindicates its hardware whereas organization reveals its performances.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">For\r\ndesign a computer it architecture is fixed first and then its organization is\r\ndecided.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Computer\r\norganization mainly does with how particular hardware works in a computer where\r\nas computer architecture deals with how to design a circuit for such hardware.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Computer\r\narchitecture is made (design) independently where as computer architecture is\r\ndesigned on the principle of certain computer architecture.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:90.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:W